channel.title: Just a throwin it out there question
channel.description:
Hello Moparscapian's, I just wanna ask,
You notice in server downloads there is 317s loading ### Maps and Cache 508s loading ### maps etc etc
I was wondering, is it possible to go backwards? Example: 667 loading 317 maps <- Lol
It sounds crazy but would it be possible?

item.title: Just a throwin it out there question
item.dc:creator: @ranger_squad ranger squad
item.description:
@ranger_squad wrote:

Yes, the maps have been released in a modified cache. I have a computer in my attic that hasn’t accessed the internet since 2005 and so I got the whole cache from there.

Read full topic
